show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Jane's ex and high school rival get engaged, inviting her to humiliate her. Jane hires a "ride-share driver" named Mike as a fake husband, unaware he's wealthy and knows her. Jane enters high society, loved by Mike but facing pressure from wealthy heiress Sissy, who opposes their union, leading to a tangled web of love, family, and jealousy.
